# Custom wiring diagrams directory
# Place user-specific or project-specific wiring configurations here
# Files in this directory are not tracked in version control (except .gitkeep)
#
# Example custom configurations:
#   - debug.jsonl: Debug mode with extra logging modules enabled
#   - benchmark.jsonl: Performance testing configuration
#   - demo.jsonl: Simplified configuration for demonstrations
#   - project_xyz.jsonl: Project-specific module selection
#
# Format: JSONL with entity, relation, config, module_enable, and parameter_override entries
